short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: RSS Feed Viewer for Feed Wrangler

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Corral provides a simple, keyboard-driven browsing experience. Jump across feeds then dive into stories one-handed while enjoying a snack.

Install the extension, sign in with your Feed Wrangler credentials and your good to go. I don’t transmit or store any of your information — enjoy.

Key Commands:
left-arrow, a, j: previous feed
right-arrow, d, l: next feed
up-arrow, w, i: previous post
down-arrow, s, k: next post

e, o: open post in new tab
r: toggle read/unread
